{"tid":1500302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］觀塘區巴士教學","createTime":"2019-08-24T03:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:57:27.000Z","uid":244417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39b406bf59e3e8a8b55f258c33e4840d129be7fb","tid":1500302,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"我見到有post話遊行喺彩虹開始，請自行決定你自己喺邊度開始行。我呢度係俾啲唔想行咁多嘅人一啲巴士路線選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會經過「創紀之城」巴士站嘅巴士線有：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSoTzBa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSoTzBa.png&h=d9c51f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AY7hgPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAY7hgPw.png&h=17d0f9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/it5KGgb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fit5KGgb.png&h=dfac5270&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQy0Y2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQy0Y2S.png&h=65d78526&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMh1gc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMh1gc.png&h=84dcb662&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6Qe3uy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6Qe3uy.png&h=5fbb81b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL9b5HU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL9b5HU.png&h=5f7169a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSdHsWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSdHsWe.png&h=8b1f409b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（當然N車可以ignore）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94fCgQd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94fCgQd.png&h=6015d2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據Google Map，步行11分鐘到。<br />\n<br />\n對於懶惰嘅你，觀塘海濱都有巴士站。想直接去海濱公園，可以坐呢啲巴士線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhu3WQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuhu3WQH.png&h=dbe7a278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nAefNXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAefNXn.png&h=8b760fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行都唔洗行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1cfcc73a6fa4a77b3d948a2fc7c9cbf04e30be94","tid":1500302,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3272d8a72de90487fbe2d712c395e0e50e233151","tid":1500302,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae24bb0199bb626f15fd503c9ba02cf91fc03e31","tid":1500302,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<code>&mdash;&mdash;-824觀塘 721元朗恐怖襲擊 811黑警還眼-&mdash;-&mdash;     我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"7d9667911f33af632bba966e24a6cb4342cc62e9","tid":1500302,"uid":283418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3272d8a72de90487fbe2d712c395e0e50e233151","tid":1500302,"uid":244417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a6f848a664ed61311328844d74449354d26bccb","tid":1500302,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/af2pGm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faf2pGm6.jpg&h=7ea205bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GWJWVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GWJWVr.jpg&h=6b684721&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/